                    <p><strong>Data Generation Commands:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><code>[GenRespawnList</code> - Generate bestiary list</li>
                        <li><code>[GenSpawnerList</code> - Generate XML spawner locations</li>
                        <li><code>[GenRegionList</code> - Generate named regions list</li>
                        <li><code>[PushRespawnStats</code> - Save spawn statistics for heatmap</li>
